Frazier EATON, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 19841. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit. Aug. 5, 1965. Frazier M. Eaton, in pro. per. Wm. N. Goodwin, U. S. Atty., Ronald G. Neubauer, Asst. U. S. Atty., Seattle, Wash., for appellee.

Before ORR, JERTBERG and MERRILL, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
